label: @ACSDECISION
description:
This variable is a true/false flag to determine if a member qualifies for a specific service.

Reference this variable in the APPROVE state.

label: @ACSDESCRIPTION
description:
This variable returns the value of the Description field from a specific service parameter.

Reference this variable in either the SFW or the SALESHISTORY states.

label: @ACSLOANAMOUNT
description:
This variable contains the loan balance of an item acquired from the credit report.

Reference this variable in either the APPROVE or the FINISH states.

label: @ACSLOANPAYMENT

Reference this variable in either the APPROVE or the FINISH states.

label: @ACSLOANRATE

label: @ACSLOANTERM

Reference this variable in any state.
